{"tid":2010564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13做咩記者？","createTime":"2020-05-10T13:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T15:32:19.000Z","uid":278351,"like":5,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fdd9ba1c35d1f58d60913227f837159c9c7b1a","tid":2010564,"uid":278351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"13歲出來？<br />\n係好勇敢，<br />\n但咁就係記者？<br />\n個個人戴住個證、着住件衫就係記者？<br />\n到底識唔識尊重記者呢個專業？<br />\n<br />\n之前有個記者真係講得好啱，<br />\n一堆魚蝦蟹將以為揸機影下野就係記者，<br />\n又落場亂咁屌狗，<br />\n你哋係喺度扼殺呢份專業。<br />\n工作表現中立<br />\n咁做先會令記者得到尊重。<br />\n<br />\n係好嬲嘅，<br />\n除咗件衫同個證先屌狗啦。<br />\n希望13歲嗰個朋友仔繼續抗爭<br />\n但係唔好再扮記者，專重專業。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528aeef05e671a5864084f8171b65b9e56e31507","tid":2010564,"uid":177213,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ci7eXTE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fci7eXTE.png&h=f4cb393c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mr3RdE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mr3RdE.png&h=6ec03a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbepAFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbepAFk.png&h=2e4e62f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5028ff21e8e06c4d75cd34644e0493f6ef816a5d","tid":2010564,"uid":3852,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"勿回, 拉"},{"pid":"e21b45d2ea795145b03b530d6a51b7c00c8db43f","tid":2010564,"uid":30604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"咁你做咩五毛？"},{"pid":"81fd52f5556db0d7aad9edb8ed5ac2a909e991da","tid":2010564,"uid":5929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"人地好似冇屌狗<br />\n出多次個post 啦"},{"pid":"509cf445d9c040f115e3abca82f0c3e4a